7. The quiet truth underneath what you’re feeling

You’re sensing this:

We shouldn’t blindly follow default biological drives
but we also shouldn’t ignore them completely

That tension is real.

The move isn’t to pick one—it’s to choose consciously which layer you’re optimizing for:
	•	genetic
	•	cultural
	•	structural
	•	personal

Most people never make that explicit—they just drift.

